docs/sdp-cli-findings-report.md:180:The integrity checker runs as part of the verify phase and treats format violations identically to semantic failures. A task that adds correct code without a docstring gets the same "ESCALATED" verdict as a task that produces broken code.
docs/startup-wizard.md:116:- Titles and hooks are now more semantically aligned too. If the hook is about light or lines, the generated song title is more likely to live in that same image field at both the modifier and noun level, and the live planner now also nudges those titles by cadence, harmony profile, and hook type so quiet settling songs and brighter kinetic songs do not keep getting the same label.
